RasPiBinaryDecoder
==================

Looks for HIGH/LOW/BASE values from GPIO pin 18 of a RaspberryPi and translates binary into displayed string
tagline: Looks for HIGH/LOW/BASE values from GPIO pin 18 of a RaspberryPi and translates binary into displayed string
